About this item

  • APP and IR Remote Contorl: With a stable bluetooth connection,control your LED lights,freely change in 16 million colors,adjust brightness,customize modes (Flashing,Jump,Fade,etc) in different speeds.
  • Music Sync: The built-in mic make the LED lights color-changing with the ambient music,easily create party atmosphere.
  • Timing Setting: The Led strip will turn on/off automatically at the setting time, repeat this seting on date you set.
  • Widely use: The led strip lights 100FT is long enough, perfect for decorating your bedroom, kitchen, ceiling, living room . Widely used on holidays and party (such as christmas, halloween,birthday,wedding .etc )
  • Easily Setup: Tear off strong adhesive tape on light strips,stick the strip lights on a clean,dry surface,finish in minutes.

    Product Description

    Come on,Light up with KSIPZE!


    Easily transforming different atmosphere for same space. Do whatever you want in minutes:Candlelight,Romantic,Dating,Movie,Festival and Party. Usually used in bedroom,living room, kitchen,mirror,bar,book store,etc.

    What you get:

    • LED strip lights
    • Remote
    • Adapter
    • Control box
    • User manual

    Smart APP LED Strip Lights

    - Easy Install in Minutes:Tear off and stick the strip lights on a clean,dry surface

    - DUAL Control: Both APP and IR Remote,Use Conveniently

    - Freely change in 16 million colors,adjust brightness

    - Flashing,Jump or Fade in different speeds

    - Music Sync: The built-in mic make the LED lights color-changing with the ambient music

    - Timing Setting: Set to turn on/off at specified time, and repeat this seting on date you set

    Customize Your Lighting, Decorate your life!

    Music Sync

    The built-in mic make the LED lights color-changing with the ambient music,easily create party atmosphere.

    Timing Setting

    The Led strip will turn on/off automatically at the setting time, repeat this seting on date you set.

    16 Million Colors

    Not only equipped with light colors like RGB (Red, green, blue), white and other 16 colors, but also 16 millions colors provide endless decor options.

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

    Amazon Customer
    5 out of 5 stars
    Totally Worth it
    I was a little scared about these lights at first, as I've bought some bad quality LEDs before. However, these are great, especially considering that I bought 100 feet of them for less than $10. They do everything that they are advertised to do. I will admit that the remote control doesn't work the best at times, you have limited options of color variations on the remote control and the remote has to be pointed towards the plug in order for it to work which means it has a limited range, but the app works pretty good , there's so many options for colors and it will sync up to the music you play which is really fun, it's like a dance party. You can use other led remotes for it as well but the remote will work the same as the one that came with the lights, you don't get more options by using a different remote. Also, the Bluetooth connection to the lights will not interfere with the connection to other Bluetooth devices which is great. I just wanted to cover the top of my wall but I had like half a roll left after that so I decided to cover the bottom as well. It took maybe an hour or two for me to install them. I love them, my room looks so fire now, and I will be saving this listing for when I go to college later this year so I can buy some of these for my dorm room as well.
